   <db:para>There are also a lot of other keys and actions (that use
                                    other modifier keys than Alt). See the Microsoft and The Open
                                    Group documentation for details.</db:para>
   <db:para>The <db:link xlink:href="http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/0735605661/trolltech/t">Microsoft book</db:link> has ISBN 0735605661. The
                                    corresponding Open Group book is very hard to find, rather
                                    expensive and we cannot recommend it. However, if you really
                                    want it, ogpubs@opengroup.org might be able to help. Ask them
                                    for ISBN 1859121047.</db:para>
